            <!-- Tour Description -->
            <div class="tour-description">
                <h2>Experience Agadir from the Atlantic Ocean</h2>
                <p>Embark on an unforgettable <strong>jet ski Agadir</strong> to experience the city's stunning coastline from the best vantage point - the Atlantic Ocean! Departing from Agadir Marina, our <strong>Agadir jet ski session</strong> offers a perfect blend of relaxation, sightseeing, and water activities. See Agadir's famous 10km golden beach, historic kasbah ruins perched on the hillside, and modern marina skyline from a unique offshore perspective.</p>
                
                <p>This <strong>jet ski ride Agadir</strong> takes you along the beautiful Atlantic coast where you'll enjoy refreshing ocean breezes and stunning views of the bay. The crystal-clear Atlantic waters invite you for refreshing swims and snorkeling adventures to explore underwater marine life. Relax on deck with soft drinks, listen to music, and watch seabirds soar overhead. You might even spot sea turtles or flying fish if you're lucky!</p>
                
                <p>Whether you choose a morning cruise, afternoon adventure, or romantic sunset sailing, our <strong>Agadir marina jet ski</strong> offers something magical. Feel the gentle rocking of waves, breathe in fresh ocean air, and disconnect from the busy beach crowds. It's the perfect relaxing escape that's still conveniently close to Agadir!</p>

                <h3>What Makes Our Agadir Jet Ski Special?</h3>
                <p>Unlike crowded beach activities, our <strong>jet ski sessions Agadir</strong> offer intimate experiences with small groups (maximum 25 passengers) on comfortable, well-maintained vessels. Our experienced captains know the best routes along the coastline, safe swimming areas, and stunning photo opportunities with Agadir's skyline as your backdrop.</p>
                
                <p>Your friendly crew shares local knowledge about Agadir's fishing traditions, maritime history, and coastal landmarks. They'll assist with swimming and snorkeling, point out marine life and seabirds, and ensure everyone - from young children to grandparents - has a memorable and safe time on the water. Life jackets provided for all passengers!</p>
                
                <p>The <strong>Agadir jet ski ride</strong> is perfect for families with children, couples seeking romance, groups of friends, and anyone wanting to see Agadir from a different angle. No sailing experience needed - just bring your sense of adventure, camera, swimsuit, and enthusiasm for the ocean!</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Detailed Itinerary -->
            <div class="itinerary-section">
                <h2 style="font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 700; color: #1F2937; margin-bottom: 30px;">Detailed Itinerary: Your Jet Ski Adventure</h2>
                
                <div class="itinerary-item">
                    <div class="itinerary-time">9:30 AM - 10:00 AM</div>
                    <h4 class="itinerary-title">Meet at Agadir Marina</h4>
                    <p style="color: #6B7280; line-height: 1.8;">Arrive at Agadir Marina (hotel pickup available for an additional fee or meet us directly at the marina). Check in with our friendly crew, receive your life jacket, and board our comfortable boat. Get settled, meet fellow passengers, and receive a safety briefing from the captain. The excitement begins!</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="itinerary-item">
                    <div class="itinerary-time">10:00 AM - 10:30 AM</div>
                    <h4 class="itinerary-title">Departure & Coastal Cruise Begins</h4>
                    <p style="color: #6B7280; line-height: 1.8;">Set sail from Agadir Marina into the beautiful Atlantic Ocean! Feel the ocean breeze as we cruise along Agadir's stunning 10km beach. See the city's skyline, modern marina, and historic kasbah ruins from the water - perfect photo opportunities! Your crew shares information about Agadir's coastal history and points out landmarks along the shore.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="itinerary-item">
                    <div class="itinerary-time">10:30 AM - 11:15 AM</div>
                    <h4 class="itinerary-title">Cruise Along Agadir Bay & Marine Life Spotting</h4>
                    <p style="color: #6B7280; line-height: 1.8;">Cruise further along the beautiful Agadir bay enjoying Atlantic waters and coastal scenery! Watch for seabirds soaring overhead, flying fish jumping from waves, and sea turtles (if lucky!). Your crew points out Agadir's key landmarks from the water - the kasbah on the hill, the new marina development, and the city's distinctive architecture. Relax, take photos, and enjoy the peaceful ocean atmosphere. This tranquil cruise is why guests love our Agadir jet ski sessions!</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="itinerary-item">
                    <div class="itinerary-time">11:15 AM - 12:00 PM</div>
                    <h4 class="itinerary-title">Swimming & Snorkeling Stop</h4>
                    <p style="color: #6B7280; line-height: 1.8;">Anchor in a calm, safe area for swimming and snorkeling! Jump into the refreshing Atlantic Ocean - the water is clearer away from the beach. Snorkeling equipment provided to explore underwater - spot colorful fish and marine life. Non-swimmers can relax on deck, sunbathe, or enjoy the floating experience. Crew assists and ensures everyone's safety. Pure ocean bliss!</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="itinerary-item">
                    <div class="itinerary-time">12:00 PM - 12:30 PM</div>
                    <h4 class="itinerary-title">Relaxation & Refreshments</h4>
                    <p style="color: #6B7280; line-height: 1.8;">Return to the boat for relaxation time. Dry off, enjoy complimentary soft drinks and light snacks, and soak in the peaceful ocean atmosphere. Perfect time for sunbathing on deck, taking more photos, or simply enjoying the gentle rocking of the boat. Listen to waves, feel the breeze, and experience true Atlantic relaxation.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="itinerary-item">
                    <div class="itinerary-time">12:30 PM - 1:00 PM</div>
                    <h4 class="itinerary-title">Return Cruise to Agadir Marina</h4>
                    <p style="color: #6B7280; line-height: 1.8;">Begin the leisurely cruise back to Agadir Marina. Take final photos of the coastline, reflect on your swimming adventures, and enjoy the last moments on the water. The crew shares final stories about Agadir's fishing traditions and maritime history. Watch the shoreline gradually get closer as we return to port.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="itinerary-item">
                    <div class="itinerary-time">1:00 PM - 1:15 PM</div>
                    <h4 class="itinerary-title">Arrival at Marina - Tour Ends</h4>
                    <p style="color: #6B7280; line-height: 1.8;">Dock back at Agadir Marina after a wonderful 3-hour Atlantic adventure! Disembark with amazing memories, beautiful photos, and the refreshed feeling that only ocean time can give. The afternoon is still young - perfect timing for lunch at marina restaurants or returning to your hotel. This relaxing boat experience is the perfect complement to Agadir's beach activities!</p>
                </div>
            </div>

